TranRunJLiteSamples
Class MultiMotor

java.lang.Object
  TranRunJLiteSamples.MultiMotor

public class MultiMotor
extends java.lang.Object

Collects information for a set of motors so that they can be operated in a synchronized way (or, independently, if desired) This version assumes that each motor has its own simulation object. That is, that the motors are not dynamically connected. If they are, a different structure would be needed.

Author:
DMAuslander, Sept. 10, 09
